* Guidance for patients and providers on operationalizing the Joint Principles was made available.<ref name=Ginsburg2008>{{cite journal |author=Ginsburg PB, Maxfield M, O'Malley AS, Peikes D, Pham HH |url=http://www.hschange.com/CONTENT/1030/1030.pdf |title=Making medical homes work: moving from concept to practice  |journal=[[Policy Perspective]] |publisher=Center for Studying Health System Change |location=Washington, DC |date=2008 Dec |volume=1 |pages=1–20 |accessdate=2009-07-10}}</ref>
